<br>
One is to have a pally/SK as main tank becasue of their ability to taunt then have whatever rogues along and having them watch their damage output.  I really doubt a warrior could taunt well enough remain tanking especially considering the impending nerf to 'defensive' which will make it even more difficult for the warrior to taunt.<br>
