Please don't forget the PvP server rogues when looking at class balance issues.<br>
<br>
What I would like to see:<br>
1. Evade dropping you from your opponent's target list (non group members only).<br>
2. Damage shields no longer giving you damage when you use range weapons.<br>
3. An escape option (be it a &quot;burst of speed&quot; or a way to &quot;sneak away&quot; without being seen with See Invis).<br>
<br>
Consider evade dropping a rogue from a target list.  This will help combat casters using the semi recently implemented /target command... which casters have been abusing to cast on rogues who can not see them. I have explained how this was done in earlier posts and have tested it myself with my own caster characters. If you would like further information feel free to email me as I would rather not repeat it in a public forum.<br>
<br>
